77-379.Tax Expenditure Reporting Act, how cited.

Sections 77-379 to 77-385 shall be known and may be cited as the Tax Expenditure Reporting Act.

SourceLaws 1979, LB 17, § 1;R.S.Supp.,1979, § 77-353;Laws 1980, LB 834, § 20;Laws 1991, LB 82, § 1.
